window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Sam and his guild mates have been grinding hard to prepare for the first Guild Wars Tournament. </p> <p>Now, the time has come. </p> <p>Sixty-four guilds will enter, but only one will emerge victorious. </p> <p>The prize: A new kingdom in the latest Rebirth Online expansion, and all the riches that go with it. </p> <p>But competing as a seven player guild isn't going to be easy, and just when the guild begins to find a rhythm, the demon Megulla informs Sam that he's a demon baby daddy a thousand times over. </p> <p>And Sam thought things were complicated before.... </p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
